items.badge_description: You have a keen taste for this Belgian masterpiece. Did you know the Saison style beer was invented by Belgian farms, brewed in the Winter and served the Spring/Summer to all their workers? Well now you do! That’s 5 different Farmhouse Ales! Try 5 more for Level 2.

items.checkin_comment: The Riesling barrel version. Super dry but so damn tasty. Nice wine influence from the barrel and no hint of the abv. Had a sneaky boilermaker with some Caol Ila.
